metadata.name: Surging Swell
metadata.description: The ocean is a captivating and ever-changing force of nature, and one of the most intriguing aspects of it is the endless array of textures it produces. The way the water swirls, ebbs, and flows can create an almost hypnotic effect, leaving me transfixed and mesmerized by its movements. As an artist, I'm inspired by these textures and wanted to try and artistically replicate them through the use of AI.
